Educational Purpose Only

This project is provided solely for educational, research, and authorized security awareness training purposes. It is intended to demonstrate wireless network security concepts and help students, researchers, and cybersecurity professionals understand how Evil Twin attacks operate and how they can be detected and prevented.

By using this software, you agree to:

Use it only in controlled laboratory environments or on networks you own or have explicit permission to test.
Comply with all applicable laws, regulations, and institutional policies.
Not use this project to gain unauthorized access to systems, intercept communications, collect credentials, or disrupt services.
Accept full responsibility for your actions and any consequences resulting from the use of this software.

